# Deploy to live (R&R / forge-cad)

After any code change in `forge-cad/`, **commit and push to `main`** before considering the task done. Local-only changes are not live.

## Required end-of-task workflow

1. Run tests if you changed behavior (`npm run test:unit` at minimum).
2. `git status` — confirm what changed.
3. `git add` + `git commit` with a clear message.
4. `git push origin main`.
5. Tell the user the commit SHA and that GitHub Pages will redeploy in 1–3 min.

## Live URLs (auto-deploy on push to `main`)

- PWA: https://solexecution.github.io/randr/
- Single-file: https://solexecution.github.io/randr/RandR.html

## Notes

- Git repo root is `forge-cad/` (not the parent `3d/` folder).
- CI builds `RandR.html` on deploy (`.github/workflows/deploy.yml`); push source only.
- Do not leave completed work uncommitted unless the user explicitly asks to hold it.
